original_title: Cygnus and the Sea Monsters: One Night in Chicago
overview: Dream Theater drummer, Mike Portnoy, and his Rush tribute band Cygnus and the Sea Monsters live CD/DVD of its one-off performance from September of 2005 in Chicago. Tracklist: 1. 2112 / 2. Cygnus X-1 / 3. Hemispheres / 4. YYZ (with Drum Solo)
title: Cygnus and the Sea Monsters: One Night in Chicago
